<p>12 只装的 Nevarro Nummies 价格为 49.95 美元（ 约人民币 327 元）。</p>
<h4><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2020/11/23/queens-gambit-viewership/">《后翼弃兵》成 Netflix 史上最受欢迎迷你剧</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381406" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review.jpg" alt="" width="1998" height="1332" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review.jpg 1998w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1998px) 100vw, 1998px" /></p>
<p>TechCrunch 消息，《后翼弃兵》在上线 28 天后，以 6200 万家庭播放成为 Netflix 史上最多人观看的迷你剧。如进行跨类别对比，该剧的播放则仍低于电视剧《猎魔人》（7600 万播放）和纪录片《养虎为患》（6400 万播放）。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B0%86%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%A0%81%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%87%AD%E8%AF%81%23&amp;Refer=top">不得将健康码作为人员通行唯一凭证</a></h4>
<p>国办发文指出，各地不得将「健康码」作为人员通行的唯一凭证，对老年人等群体可采取凭有效身份证件登记、持纸质证明通行、出示「通信行程卡」作为辅助行程证明等替代措施。有条件的地区和场所要为不使用智能手机的老年人设立「无健康码通道」，做好服务引导和健康核验。</p>
<p>网友：「文件有了，下一步好好落实基层才是最重要的。」「希望不要把老年人扔在信息时代后面，毕竟我们以后也会老啊，也会有跟不上时代的那一天。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357581" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>John Lewis 圣诞广告：《Give a Little Love》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381361" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
